# Generated by hatch-vcs at build time
src/chime/_version.py

# uv resolves and writes this lockfile on `uv run`/`uv sync`. chime is a
# library (loose deps in pyproject, zero-runtime-deps pitch), not an app, so
# the lockfile isn't committed — ignore it so it never dirties the tree or
# blocks a release preflight.
uv.lock

docs/*